    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are each justified as not required at MRL 2 for a Class II CPB device. The CFD hemolysis model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the CPB operating envelope of the FDA generic centrifugal pump. The assessment supports regulatory submission for pre-market review.",
